nl.tue.fingerpaint.testenvironment

Class StandardCapabilitiesProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tue.fingerpaint.testenvironment.StandardCapabilitiesProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CapabilitiesProvider

    public class StandardCapabilitiesProvider
extends Object
implements CapabilitiesProvider
    Provides the standard set of browsers and Dimension's used in the test environment for the Fingerpaint project. Currently the browsers in the standard testing environment are the newest versions of:
    • Mozilla Firefox
    • Microsoft Internet Explorer
    • Opera Chrome
    • Apple Safari
    Of these browser, Microsoft Internet Explorer and Apple Safari are currently running in sequential mode because of problems during multi-threading. The following dimensions are tested in the standard testing environment:
    • Desktop: 1600x900
    • Tablet horizontal: 1280x800
    • Tablet vertical: 800x1280
    • Phone horizontal: 960x540
    • Phone vertical: 540x960
    Author:
    Lasse Blaauwbroek
